{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2270812, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "信中医主要是没钱", "timestamp": 1628856297, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270818, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270812, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 啊，这😅", "timestamp": 1628856347, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270827, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "信仰自由", "timestamp": 1628856493, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270834, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "中医值得信，前提是找到水平高的。我爸是中医，感冒头疼发烧，一副药解决；胃受寒这种小毛病，都不用一副药，一味药就立竿见影。", "timestamp": 1628856549, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270841, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270834, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 我多喝热水就能解决", "timestamp": 1628856608, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270850, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270812, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 也不一定，有人会花几千块钱买一副中药", "timestamp": 1628856640, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270870, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270850, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 相比于几十万的正规方案，花几千买个希望还是容易被忽悠的", "timestamp": 1628856790, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270884, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270850, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 而且不少在接受正规治疗的同时接受中医治疗有疗效的也很有说服力", "timestamp": 1628856892, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270887, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我也信，附近有个很有名的老中医，小时候经常吃中药，效果很好", "timestamp": 1628856941, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270890, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270870, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 什么治疗方案能有几十万？晚期癌症多次化疗无效之后？\n接受正规治疗同时接受中医治疗有疗效能说明什么", "timestamp": 1628856999, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270906, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "没问题，前提是不像饭圈那样无脑捧&无脑黑", "timestamp": 1628857196, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270909, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270890, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 一个成功率很高的癌症治疗都要几十万啊", "timestamp": 1628857202, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270914, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "有时候效果还挺好，不信还真不行", "timestamp": 1628857249, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270920, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "如果你不信，也请尊敬它，就像鬼神一样，敬鬼神而不信鬼神", "timestamp": 1628857286, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270922, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270890, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 我的意思是接受正规治疗同时接受中医治疗有疗效被归结为中医（甚至不一定是中医可能只是骗子）的治疗效果", "timestamp": 1628857309, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270931, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270920, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 可不敢敬，打中医幌子行骗太容易了，法律风险也不高", "timestamp": 1628857400, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270955, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270931, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 展开讲讲", "timestamp": 1628857773, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2270988, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270920, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 针对鬼神，难道不该持“破除迷信”的态度吗……", "timestamp": 1628857918, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271016, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270988, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 如果你在类似于北京、西安这样比较有悠久历史的地方生活过，可能就不会说出类似的话了\n顺带一提，鬼魂/魂魄这种东西是真的存在的，我见到过", "timestamp": 1628858063, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271058, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271016, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 你这句话中的“东西”的含义，更接近“物质”“物体”“物理现象”还是别的什么呢？", "timestamp": 1628858320, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271074, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271016, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 确实，什么叫做“存在”，什么叫做“见过”，都不好说", "timestamp": 1628858455, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271085, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270909, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 癌症这个东西都有标准的治疗规范的，你再有钱也得一步一步来，哪有直接上最贵的药的。", "timestamp": 1628858511, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271086, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271058, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 现象以及人的感受，例如在半山腰听见山崖下越来越近的哭声，余光以及眼睛失焦后观察到的有明显意图的白色浮动半透明物等等", "timestamp": 1628858514, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271090, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271074, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: yep，毕竟这种东西没真正体验过是不会信的。只不过真的不希望更多的人去体验它，所以怀有一颗敬畏的心总是没错的。", "timestamp": 1628858566, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271098, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271058, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 其实想获得一个比较低level的体验，可以在圆明园待到晚上（虽然会广播闭园但其实没人管，出门也正常出）", "timestamp": 1628858650, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271099, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2270909, "tag": null, "text": "树洞居然也有grace这种信跳大神的人，也难怪信中医的这么多了", "timestamp": 1628858662, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271102, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271098, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: （10点过", "timestamp": 1628858671, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271107, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271099, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: 没见过当然不信咯，还是那句话，可以不信但希望你敬畏它。", "timestamp": 1628858709, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271108, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "宗教信仰自由", "timestamp": 1628858726, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271110, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271086, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 白色浮动半透明物，我想你可能也是飞蚊症病友。我也是", "timestamp": 1628858751, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271114, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271086, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 那个白色浮动的东西是眼睛的玻璃体并不完全均质导致的。至于哭声，我没经历过，我不清楚……", "timestamp": 1628858763, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271115, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271102, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 可不敢，你不怕流浪汉，丐帮，吸毒者，嫖娼者吗", "timestamp": 1628858767, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271118, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271107, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 我不敬畏，打倒一切牛鬼蛇神。封建迷信害的人还不够多吗", "timestamp": 1628858793, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271122, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271115, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 我不敢晚上去僻静的地方，可不是怕这些，可怕的人太多了", "timestamp": 1628858820, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271124, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271110, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: （每个人都会有轻微的这种情况。患飞蚊症的人，这种情况会显著增多）", "timestamp": 1628858829, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271126, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271114, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 哭声估计是猫叫😅", "timestamp": 1628858848, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271139, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "至于Grace所说的历史悠久的地方，我在南京住过一段时间，在历史悠久这方面南京城算是第一梯队的了。这种经历没在我身上复现。", "timestamp": 1628858947, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271141, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271090, "tag": null, "text": "简单说就是，现代科学所涉足的领域还是不完全的，面对诸如人体、灵魂之类并无积累，这时一些传统经验会起到作用，中医就在此列。但希望现代科学能尽早整合取代这些传统经验。这是我的看法。", "timestamp": 1628858979, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271144, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不错不错，果然青年们的情绪是最容易被煽动起来的。\n\n我在不同的社群中都尝试过类似的实验，想看看不同年龄段的人，对于那个年龄段所不接受的观念的态度。\n\n谢谢大家愿意聊这个话题，实验结束。", "timestamp": 1628859030, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271148, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "还是那句话，别太自以为是，敬畏宇宙和自然总没错。", "timestamp": 1628859089, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271149, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢大家，再见啦", "timestamp": 1628859099, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271160, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271114, "tag": null, "text": "grace年纪多大了，是不是借号混进来的啊😅", "timestamp": 1628859231, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2271232, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271148, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 人们敬畏自然，只是因为至今为止人们还没战胜自然。\n但是，相对于人类的发展速度来说，自然的变化速度可以忽略。《愚公移山》中说，“而山不加增，何苦而不平？”地球上的这个大自然的力量，在今天看来还很伟大，但也即将在几代人的时间内被人的力量超越，伴随着的是“敬畏自然”这个自古流传的神话的破灭。\n基督徒为什么提出“上帝的归上帝，凯撒的归凯撒”这种“毫不虔诚”的话？因为凯撒大帝的大军他们打不过。对大自然的敬畏，也只是人类现在面对大自然的权宜之计。", "timestamp": 1628860140, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2272108, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": 2271149, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 别走啊，还没看够呢😋", "timestamp": 1628867936, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2273550, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "那为什么中国鬼魂和外国鬼魂不一样呢", "timestamp": 1628880457, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2468764, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 437123, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "信鬼神的生病的时候找个神婆跳一跳就行了", "timestamp": 1631193632, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 8, "pid": 437123, "reply": 46, "tag": null, "text": "爸妈对中医深信不疑怎么办", "timestamp": 1628856158, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1631193630, "url": "", "vote": {}}}